      <title>OpenAI 与《人物》杂志出版商签署许可协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/openai-inks-deal-with-people-magazine-publisher-dotdash-meredith</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 已与 Dotdash Meredith 签署了一项许可协议，该协议将把《人物》杂志出版商的内容带到 ChatGPT 上，并帮助训练这家科技初创公司的人工智能模型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/openai-inks-deal-with-people-magazine-publisher-dotdash-meredith</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:43:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
